Pre-Apocalypse[]: Nothing is known about Dinesh's life prior to or as the outbreak began.
Post-Apocalypse[]: At some point in the apocalypse, Dinesh joined a community called the Alexandria Safe Zone . As the Wolves invade Alexandria, ransacking homes and murdering residents, Dinesh is captured by a Wolf. With his hands bound, he is led through the streets of Alexandria as a captive before he is eventually killed by his captor and left on the porch of a house. The next day, Dinesh's body is gathered by Tobin and Bruce and buried along with the other slain Alexandrians. His name is then added to the memorial wall by Betsy and two other women.
Death[]: Killed By Aaron (Indirectly Caused) Aaron leaves his backpack at Del Arno Foods, which causes the Wolves to locate and attack Alexandria. The Wolves As the Wolves make their way into Alexandria, Dinesh is one of the many residents to be killed.
